data.description: Everything you want, location, yard, shop and lots of room. 45 min to Nashville airport, 15 miles to Gallatin, Lebanon, 1 hr to Bowling Green & Nashville. Beautiful Fenced yard with a remote controlled security gate. This Home has a split layout complete with a 18x18 Florida room. Walk in closets. Lots of cabinets in the kitchen including a pantry. All Appliances stay including Washer/Dryer. A nice 12x18 covered porch to enjoy your morning drink. Storm shelter. 1 car detached garage/shop 30x40 fully wired & insulated. Plus a * 20x30 carport *20x30 shed *12x18 shed. Storm shelter. A dream come true, So much to offer! Detitled and attached. Don't let this one slip by you, come check it out today. This home is protected by a 2-10 Home Warranty available for purchase at closing. If not purchased at closing, the warranty expires the date of closing.
